Trinity::

She trusted him completely. She wasn't thrilled about going to meet 
the giant spider. She didn't like spiders. And any spider that looked 
like it could eat her in one gulp was a spider that she really 
wasnted to avoid. But, He said he was looking out for her, so what 
did she have to fear. She jumped up and onto his back.
"So what's Archangle going to be able to do? And do we really have to 
go see that spider. I"m not scared or nothing, but, I don't loike 
spiders."
